Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.28,0:00:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR]\NWealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.20,0:00:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold Roger, the King\Nof the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.86,0:00:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,attained this and everything\Nelse the world had to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.66,0:00:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And his dying words drove\Ncountless souls to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.12,0:00:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[GOLD ROGER]\NYou want my treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.70,0:00:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.04,0:00:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I left everything I gathered\Ntogether in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.21,0:00:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you just have to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR] These words lured men\Nto the Grand Line in pursuit of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.72,0:00:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,dreams greater than they've\Never dared to imagine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.01,0:00:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the time\Nknown as the Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.51,0:00:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.10,0:00:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.86,0:00:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One Piece!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.11,0:01:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compass left behind{\i0}\N{\i1}It'll only slow us down{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.58,0:01:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your heart will be your guide{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.83,0:01:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Raise the sails{\i0}\N{\i1}and take the helm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.21,0:01:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That legendary place that the{\i0}\N{\i1}end of the map reveals{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.84,0:01:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is only legendary{\i0}\N{\i1}until someone proves it real{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.60,0:01:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through it all, through all{\i0}\N{\i1}the troubled times, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.60,0:01:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}through the heartache,{\i0}\N{\i1}and through the pain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.31,0:01:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Know that I will be there{\i0}\N{\i1}to stand by you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.57,0:01:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like I know{\i0}\N{\i1}you'll stand by me! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.07,0:01:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.74,0:01:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.62,0:01:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's always room for you{\i0}\N{\i1}if you want to be my friend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:02:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are, we are on the cruise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.13,0:02:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.43,0:02:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN] I'll spare him,\Nbut you have to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.64,0:02:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't make this any\Nharder, Sanji. Just leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.27,0:02:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.73,0:02:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEARL]\NPearl... Cymbals!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.48,0:02:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.15,0:02:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEARL]\NSurprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.40,0:02:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] There's no way to repay\Nthe old geezer for his kindness,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.24,0:02:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,unless I risk my life for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.95,0:02:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already taken everything\Nelse that man holds dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.95,0:02:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,His power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.16,0:02:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,His dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] He gave up his leg\Nso that I could live!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.47,0:02:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.81,0:02:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI ] This restaurant\Nis that old man's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.18,0:02:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So, while I'm around,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna let anything\Nelse get taken from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:03:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY growls]\NNow, Gum-Gum!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghin'll shoot the old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.61,0:03:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Battle-Axe!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.08,0:03:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] "Cool-headed,\NCold-hearted, Demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,0:03:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirate Fleet Chief\NCommander, Ghin!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.30,0:03:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NHm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE A]\NHe destroyed the fin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.23,0:03:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES]\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NHe's trying to sink my ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare defy me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.78,0:03:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghin, blow his\Nhead off right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NWhat are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.16,0:03:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But... he...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He saved our lives\Nwhen we were starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.33,0:04:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He gave us food!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghin, kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.67,0:04:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.88,0:04:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see why\Nyou're all so upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.47,0:04:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't sink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[grumbling]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.52,0:04:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Back off, Chore Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not your fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.56,0:04:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NBut, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.56,0:04:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.73,0:04:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to sink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.27,0:04:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.90,0:04:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE groan]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, Cmon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] You bastard,\Nthat's what you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't sink this ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.28,0:04:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But, if the restaurant's gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.66,0:04:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no reason to\Nattack then, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.87,0:04:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NHm.Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This ship saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.08,0:04:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe everything to her and\Nyou will not take that away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna die for a\Ndumb, old restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.92,0:04:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.01,0:04:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how you wanna\Nrepay your debt?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:05:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The old man didn't save you so\Nthat you could kill yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.31,0:05:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it so you could do\Nsomething with your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.27,0:05:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to die like a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And so your big idea is\Nto help them attack us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.23,0:05:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.11,0:05:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.03,0:05:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEARL] Boys, there's no\Nneed for friends to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially when there's\Nnothing either of you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.42,0:05:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Not while there's a big shotgun
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.25,0:05:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,pressed right up against\Nthe old man's chef hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.42,0:05:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Your problem began\Nwhen you decided
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,to come up against\Nthe Krieg Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing can stop us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.76,0:05:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEARL]\NFIRE PEARLS!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you will burn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEARL laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEARL wheezing]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.20,0:05:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.20,0:06:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[groaning]\NWhat did... you do... Ghin?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Pearl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghin, you have betrayed\Nyour captain and your ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.59,0:06:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.76,0:06:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Don Krieg,\Nbut he saved our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Not like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.14,0:06:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He deserves better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He deserves to face\Ndeath standing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.64,0:06:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But I promise you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.23,0:06:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...he'll still\Ndie by my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, great...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.57,0:06:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My Chief Commander has now\Ncompletely lost his marbles.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You just hang in\Nthere, Old Zeff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.95,0:06:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARNE]\NA-Are you alright, Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He's their chief commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.08,0:06:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.21,0:06:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Did ya' see him crush\Nthat guy, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.25,0:06:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,One blow and his\Nshield was in pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.63,0:06:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, that's power!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.26,0:06:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.30,0:07:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! My plan worked perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, he's out in the open.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.97,0:07:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.14,0:07:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you thought\Nthat this would happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.77,0:07:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.81,0:07:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NSanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.31,0:07:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I'm just following orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.52,0:07:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to ruin this ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think it's\Ntoo late for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.49,0:07:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] Ha. Maybe.\NBut, if you think that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you're going to get to this\Nrestaurant without killing me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.78,0:07:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you got another thing coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.70,0:07:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it will be an absolute\Npleasure to kill you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.87,0:07:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...my good friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee... that's comforting...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.71,0:07:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.92,0:07:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NYou as well, Chore Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.21,0:07:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NGee... thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.80,0:07:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I'm not afraid\Nof any Krieg pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.84,0:07:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.76,0:07:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES grumble]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.05,0:07:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE B]\NYa' little twerp!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.14,0:07:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE C] Get ready\Nto die, little man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.73,0:07:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna stuff that\Nstupid straw hat
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,right down your throat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE D]\NWe're the Krieg Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.10,0:07:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Rulers of the East Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.61,0:07:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Only 'cause you outnumbered the\Nother pirates in the East Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy... now you\Nreally pissed 'em off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.16,0:08:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.37,0:08:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE]\NYou're dead meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold your place!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.75,0:08:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE E]\NBut, Don Krieg!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.34,0:08:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE F]\NHe can't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NYou only prove his point
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,when you lose control or\Nwhine like little babies!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You see me trembling with anger?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.93,0:08:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the weak react\Nto mere words.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don Krieg Pirates\Nrun from no man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.98,0:08:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES]\NYes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.19,0:08:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[KREIG]\NGhin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.15,0:08:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.15,0:08:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG] It's your job to\Ntake care of that cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.07,0:08:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll handle the little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.28,0:08:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That brat is all mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.37,0:08:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Don Krieg.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NHey, Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.08,0:08:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can try your Devil\NFruit magic against me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've seen it all before
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:09:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and have never been\Ndefeated by such trickery.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,When you experience\Nthe full force
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.97,0:09:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,that conquered the\Nentire East Blue,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.30,0:09:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,then you'll understand the\Nmeaning of power, Chore Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.14,0:09:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Your voice is getting\Non my nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.81,0:09:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna to kick your ass!\NIt's as simple as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.48,0:09:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on just a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.03,0:09:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG growls]\NThe impudence!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.21,0:09:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE G]\NThat cook is done for  now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.38,0:09:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE H] Yeah man, when\NGhin takes out his weapons,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.97,0:09:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,he's through screwing\Naround. Just look at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.56,0:09:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE I] They call him,\N"The Cold-Hearted Demon."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE J K] He's our\Ncool-headed, cold-hearted,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:10:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,pirate fleet chief\Ncommander, Ghin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.65,0:10:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if\Nyou beg for mercy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.86,0:10:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll still laugh in your\Nface while he kills you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.41,0:10:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN] I'm sorry, Sanji,\Nbut I can't be defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.62,0:10:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, go ahead...\Ntell yourself that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NHere I come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,--[GHIN grunts]\N--[SANJI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.55,0:10:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NHa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.68,0:10:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.60,0:10:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,--[SANJI grunts]\N--[GHIN chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NYou son of a--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.94,0:10:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NHa. Ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.40,0:10:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI gulps, grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.49,0:10:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.20,0:10:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NI warned you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but you just wouldn't listen,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:10:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.33,0:10:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI huffs]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NHeh. And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.67,0:11:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.67,0:11:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...it's time for you\Nto accept defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES cheering]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.89,0:11:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK WALLA gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.65,0:11:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.37,0:11:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.71,0:11:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.46,0:11:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH grunt]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[CREWS chattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE L] That cook...\Nkicked Ghin in the head!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.62,0:12:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE M]\NYeah, I couldn't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.37,0:12:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think he's still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.46,0:12:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NEnough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.96,0:12:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,After all this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.71,0:12:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,you should know a hell of a lot\Nbetter than that, you idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.17,0:12:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a reason I trust him
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,above any of my\Nother pirate crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghin is always a cool-headed,\Ncold-hearted Demon
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and he never quits!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.85,0:12:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe\NSanji is getting up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He should lie back down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.11,0:12:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,After what he's been through,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.32,0:12:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,his ribs must be\Ncompletely smashed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.74,0:13:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... that... wasn't...\Ntoo bad... Chief Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.29,0:13:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] Lemme know when\Nyou're ready to really fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.42,0:13:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NHmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.68,0:13:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHe's just sitting there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.85,0:13:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.35,0:13:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it's ass kickin' time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.03,0:13:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hurt yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.28,0:13:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.66,0:13:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps, screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.13,0:13:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to fight me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.34,0:13:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.63,0:13:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I really have to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.26,0:13:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If all I want to do is kill\Nyou, that's enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.76,0:14:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't have any patience\Nfor your stupid games,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.73,0:14:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,little fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.02,0:14:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How about I bite your head off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.73,0:14:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,--[thudding]\N--[PIRATES laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.94,0:14:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.65,0:14:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES cheering]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]\NSanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.28,0:14:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[coughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Pfft.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.12,0:14:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE N]\NWoo hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Pulverize the rest of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.25,0:14:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE O]\NYeah, what he said!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.09,0:14:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap! If only he hadn't\Nfought that Pearl guy first!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.88,0:14:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I don't think
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.09,0:14:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll survive another hit\Nfrom those balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.72,0:14:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.01,0:14:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] Go ahead... you\Nhit like a girl, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.02,0:14:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NHe's too strong for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.91,0:15:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.12,0:15:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye, Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.66,0:15:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI, GHIN grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.04,0:15:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that? Your pity?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.25,0:15:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.13,0:15:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,--[GHIN yells]\N--[SANJI] I'm not dead yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE P]\NChief Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.59,0:15:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,--[bones cracking]\N--[SANJI groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.93,0:15:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.31,0:15:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gonna kill himself\Njust trying to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.11,0:15:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,--[bones crackling]\N--[SANJNI groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.95,0:15:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[KREIG chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES chattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NYou damn bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.63,0:16:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.51,0:16:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.93,0:16:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY, CARNE gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.40,0:16:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NI can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.70,0:16:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't obey your order.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.08,0:16:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpering continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.88,0:16:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NThis man saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.47,0:16:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't, Don Krieg!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.47,0:16:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.10,0:16:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.48,0:16:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.06,0:16:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.23,0:17:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't... do...\Nwhat... you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.82,0:17:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NTake it and leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't accept charity,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.24,0:17:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't matter how\Ndown and out I may be,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.00,0:17:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,just take this stuff away, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop your whining\Nand eat it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what\Nthey say in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.63,0:17:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,To me, if anyone's hungry,\Nthey're a customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.67,0:17:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN] Sorry, but I'm\Nnot your customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.55,0:17:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] You can die for\Nyour pride, if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But listen, if you\Nand eat and survive,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.56,0:17:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,won't that give you the\Nopportunity to fight for pride
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,truly worth having,\Nnow and in the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.98,0:17:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.36,0:17:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NI'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... thank you, so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.53,0:17:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was over, I truly\Nthought I was going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.45,0:17:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.75,0:17:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NThis food... it's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never eaten food\Nthis good before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.26,0:18:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.13,0:18:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[sobbing contiues]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.72,0:18:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. You'll probably\Nget yelled at, or fired
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.14,0:18:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,'cause you gave me\Nthat food for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.02,0:18:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now there's not proof,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.06,0:18:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,so there's no way for\Nme to get yelled at.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.81,0:18:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN] He treated me\Nwith such respect,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.07,0:18:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and decency, and kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.66,0:18:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why... I can't\Nbring myself to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.21,0:18:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get caught again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.83,0:18:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NI've always been loyal to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.38,0:18:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Up till now, I've believed\Nin what we've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.63,0:18:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I respect you and appreciate\Nall you have given me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.89,0:18:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Trusting me as your\NChief Commander
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.80,0:18:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,was the honor of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.68,0:18:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Until this moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I have obeyed every single\Norder you have given me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,without ever questioning it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.73,0:19:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't live with myself\Nif I kill this man...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.98,0:19:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I cannot break my oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.15,0:19:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, I beg you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me disobey\Njust this one order!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.45,0:19:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NDon Krieg...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.21,0:19:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't we just leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They can keep the\Nrestaurant for themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.34,0:19:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yelling] You little\Nson of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.97,0:19:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you can defy my orders\Nand then tell me what to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.98,0:19:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NIt's pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.77,0:19:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Morality, sympathy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.07,0:19:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Weaknesses I never\Nexpected to see from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.44,0:19:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not my Chief\NCommander anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.33,0:19:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.53,0:19:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Step aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.08,0:19:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Not the gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.75,0:20:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE Q]\NHe's going to use the MH5!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE R]\NWe're all gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.51,0:20:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,--What?!\N--Poison gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.17,0:20:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE S yelling]\NWhere's my mask?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.76,0:20:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE T]\NMasks on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.30,0:20:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE U]\NMove it, move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.64,0:20:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE V]\NHe's using MH5!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.01,0:20:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE A]\NGas is a coward's weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.43,0:20:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE B]\NYou bastard, you'll kill us all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.02,0:20:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing that\Nmatters in a battle
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.27,0:20:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,is who ends up winning,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.06,0:20:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,even if more have got to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.98,0:20:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Poison gas is just\Na means to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.11,0:20:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Victory is all that decides\Nwhat's right and what's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.24,0:20:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are dead, nobody's\Ngonna hear you complain anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When you don't hesitate\Nto do unspeakable,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,horrible things...\Nthat, is true power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.47,0:20:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He's insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.47,0:20:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.89,0:20:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Might as well throw\Nthat gas mask away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.52,0:21:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're no longer worthy\Nto be a Krieg Pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.52,0:21:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.82,0:21:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.45,0:21:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] I'm not going to let\Nthat happen, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.74,0:21:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wasting your\Ntime, Chore Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.25,0:21:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY yelping]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.42,0:21:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.46,0:21:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.68,0:21:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NAw, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.18,0:21:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.56,0:21:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to\Nlisten to that blowhard,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.89,0:21:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,because I'm gonna kick his ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.10,0:21:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.10,0:21:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No! My captain\Ncannot be defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.65,0:21:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don Krieg is the\Nstrongest man alive
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.36,0:21:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and I respect his punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.61,0:21:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you please snap out of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.74,0:21:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.70,0:21:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.33,0:22:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Obeying my emotions meant\Nbetraying my captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.37,0:22:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were in his position, then\NI would've done the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.38,0:22:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, death is the\Nonly honor I have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.59,0:22:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.93,0:22:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NWhy? No...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.22,0:22:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh. So, you've\Nremembered your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.72,0:22:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But, it's much\Ntoo late for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.10,0:22:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you will both die together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.65,0:22:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the MH5
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.44,0:22:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Poison...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.48,0:22:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Gas Bomb...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.73,0:22:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.70,0:22:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES chattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.37,0:22:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK Z]\NDive! Dive!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.83,0:22:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY]\NGet inside the restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.29,0:22:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,--[LUFFY] Thank you!\N--[PIRATES gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.67,0:22:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji, Ghin, catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.17,0:22:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, for mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.88,0:22:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Where'd they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.26,0:23:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.36,0:23:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a kid, I never stopped{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.74,0:23:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Searching for a great treasure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.36,0:23:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had a map in my mind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.12,0:23:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That I knew would lead me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.25,0:23:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had to find my way{\i0}\N{\i1}to that place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.96,0:23:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before someone could beat me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.46,0:23:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promised land{\i0}\N{\i1}was in my grasp{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.09,0:23:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I wouldn't let go{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.18,0:23:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My only dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.10,0:23:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't stop chasing it{\i0}\N{\i1}until it comes true{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.73,0:23:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if the world ever changes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.03,0:23:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.87,0:24:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We could return to the time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.91,0:24:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When everything's the same{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.87,0:24:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as I'm with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.13,0:24:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My memories won't fade{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.00,0:24:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Waiting for that{\i0}\N{\i1}one true dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.85,0:24:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] I'll show you\Nwhose grave this is!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.64,0:24:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Your weapons can't stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.60,0:24:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NHow come you don't flinch?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.19,0:24:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NWhat are you, stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.56,0:24:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NSay that again, I dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.40,0:24:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NWhat are you, stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.61,0:24:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NShut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.61,0:24:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NTold me to say it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.07,0:24:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.20,0:24:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"I Won't Die! Fierce\NBattle, Luffy vs. Krieg."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.74,0:24:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be\NKing of the Pirates!

